ce to food banks offering food to poorer residents.\"", "\"INNOVATION AWARD\":\"In 20X5, Robinholt University won an Innovation award for its new innovative conference facilities which have attracted a number of new clients in the last year.\"", "\"STRATEGIC AIMS OF ROBINHOLT UNIVERSITY\":\"Robinholt University's five strategic aims include providing education that promotes intellectual initiative, creating an organized and efficient learning environment, and ensuring high academic standards to prepare graduates for success in life and the workplace.\""], "parameters": {"model": "text-embedding-3-small", "temperature": 0.0, "frequency_penalty": null, "presence_penalty": null, "top_p": 1.0, "max_tokens": 4000, "n": 1}}